My vim files

1 set .vimrc

```
cd
git clone 
ln -s dot-vim-files/.vimrc .
```

2 install ctags

sudo apt-get install ctags

3 mkdir

 mkdir ~/.backup ~/.yankring_history ~/.vim/undo

4 for ruby and rails
 cp dot-vim-files/snippets ~/.vim/

5 Install plugins

mkdir -p ~/.vim/bundle
git clone https://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim ~/.vim/bundle/neobundle.vim

Launch `vim`, run `:NeoBundleInstall`    
    ( ref https://github.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim )


for vim-powerline

cd ~/.vim/bundle/vim-powerline
git checkout -b develop origin/develop
